@startuml
title Agentic Flow v2.4.0 - Actual Run Flow (Run 5 — search-enhancement-api)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Team Lead" as TL
participant "Product Manager" as PM
participant "Java Architect" as ARCH
participant "Arch Reviewer" as AREV
participant "Java Coder" as CODER
participant "Code Reviewer" as CREV

note over TL,CREV #E2E8F0
Green = passed gate
Yellow = rejected / returned
Red = red card
New in v2.4.0: Reviewer split into
Architecture Reviewer + Code Reviewer
end note

group Planning Phase [12 min, 8% context]
TL -> TL : flow-log create\n+ lock-requirements
TL -> PM : Story request
PM -[#22C55E]> TL : Story accepted\n(~2 min, Haiku)
TL -> ARCH : Create plan\n(GPT-5.4)
ARCH -> ARCH : plan-validate fails\nfix and retry
ARCH -[#22C55E]> TL : Plan accepted\n(plan v3 draft lifecycle)
end

group Architecture Review [16 min, 15% context]
TL -> AREV : Round 1\n(GPT-5.4)
AREV --> TL : 4 risks raised\n(all UNCLASSIFIED)
TL -> TL : Classify severities\n(3 HIGH, 1 MEDIUM)
TL -[#F59E0B]> ARCH : Fix risks\n(significant findings)
ARCH --> TL : Plan revised
TL -> AREV : Round 2
AREV -[#22C55E]> TL : All risks resolved\narchitecture-gate PASS
note right of AREV #D1FAE5
Severity ownership model validated:
UNCLASSIFIED → TL classifies → gate.
Dramatic improvement from Run 1
(9 rounds, 17 risks, zero delivery)
end note
end

group Implementation Phase [~25 min, 32% context]
TL -> CODER : Batch 1\n(Codex)
CODER --> TL : Batch returned
TL -[#DC2626]> TL : Red card #1\nKarate assertion failed
TL -> CODER : Fix Karate issue
CODER -> CODER : MODULE_NOT_FOUND\n(flow-log from wrong dir)
CODER --> TL : Fix returned
TL -[#DC2626]> TL : Red card #2\nKarate still fails (LABEL vs label)
note right of TL #FEF3C7
After 2 red cards on same issue,
TL routes to Architect instead of
grinding a third Coder loop
end note
TL -[#F59E0B]> ARCH : Plan correction\n(case-mapping spec gap)
ARCH --> TL : Plan corrected
TL -> CODER : Continue with\ncorrected plan
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Fix returned
end

group TL Verification [50% context]
TL -> TL : final-check + karate\nall PASS
end

group Code Review [7 min, 52% context]
TL -> CREV : Code review\n(Sonnet 4.6)
CREV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS\n(0 findings, 1 round)
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Sign-off + complete\n~84 min, 52% context
end

@enduml
